  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
create_atoms 1 box
Created 256 atoms
  using lattice units in orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (16.2 16.2 16.2)
  create_atoms CPU = 0.000 seconds

pair_style meam
pair_coeff * * library.meam AlS SiS MgS CuS FeS AlSiMgCuFe.meam AlS
Reading MEAM library file library.meam with DATE: 2012-06-29
Reading MEAM potential file AlSiMgCuFe.meam with DATE: 2012-06-29

